OL,6,FAdam Peaty says his family have
OL,7,F"encouraged" "excessive and intrusive"
OL,8,Freporting about him and his fiancee.
OL,10,FThis is the latest twist in the
OL,11,FOlympic swimmer family feud ahead of
OL,12,Fhis wedding to Holly Ramsay, daughter
OL,13,Fof celebrity chef Gordon.
OL,15,FEarlier this month, the police got
OL,16,Finvolved with two officers from
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police meeting
OL,18,FPeaty off the plane after his stag-do
OL,19,Fin Budapest.
