OL,3,CAdam Peaty says reporting of family
OL,4,Cfeud has been 'hurtful and upsetting'
OL,6,FPolice say they are investigating
OL,7,Fthreatening messages sent to the
OL,8,Fswimmer. The public order crime is now
OL,9,Fbeing dealt with by Staffordshire
OL,10,FPolice.
OL,12,FThe family row is said to have been
OL,13,Fbuilding for months and has come to a
OL,14,Fhead as Adam's mum, Caroline, was
OL,15,F'disinvited' to the December wedding.
OL,17,FShe told ITV News Central: "Family are
OL,18,Feverything to me and I'm hurt beyond
OL,19,Fbelief."
