OL,3,CAdam Peaty says reporting of family
OL,4,Cfeud has been 'hurtful and upsetting'
OL,6,FIn his first public response to the
OL,7,Frow, Adam Peaty posted on social
OL,8,Fmedia, saying: "Over the past few
OL,9,Fdays, a lot has been reported and
OL,10,Fcomments posted about the private life
OL,11,Fof Holly and myself.
OL,13,F"My sister Bethany has also been
OL,14,Ftargeted. This has been almost
OL,15,Fentirely one-sided and, in many cases,
OL,16,Fexcessive and intrusive.
