OL,3,CAdam Peaty says reporting of family
OL,4,Cfeud has been 'hurtful and upsetting'
OL,6,F"It has been hurtful and upsetting to
OL,7,Fread, especially given the false basis
OL,8,Fupon which we have been targeted. What
OL,9,Fmakes it worse is that it has been
OL,10,Fencouraged by members of my family.
OL,12,F"Bethany, Holly and I cannot go into
OL,13,Fdetails, given an ongoing police
OL,14,Finvestigation into serious matters
OL,15,Fthat arose long before recent events."
OL,17,FHe continued: "For those who know me
OL,18,Fpersonally, who know that I work so
OL,19,Fhard on trying to improve myself as a
OL,20,Fperson who wants to contribute to
OL,21,Fmaking the world a better place.
