OL,3,CAdam Peaty says reporting of family
OL,4,Cfeud has been 'hurtful and upsetting'
OL,6,F"I am continuing to learn about myself
OL,7,Fand how I can be the man I want to be;
OL,8,Fa worthy partner, father, businessman,
OL,9,Ffriend and athlete; even through these
OL,10,Fchallenging times.
OL,12,F"Bethany, Hollly and I will get
OL,13,Fthrough this - we do not ask for
OL,14,Fsympathy. We just need people to be
OL,15,Faware that there are always two sides
OL,16,Fto every story.
OL,18,F"To those of you who have reached out
OL,19,Fand shown kindness and understanding -
OL,20,Fthank you. It is deeply appreciated.
OL,21,FYours faithfully, Adam."
